quran[6{c,v,t}:
9,94,jab tum un ke paas wapas jao ge to tum se izr karen ge tum kehna ke mat izr karo hum hargiz tumhari baat nahi manen ge khuda ne hum ko tumahray sab halaat bta diye hain. aur abhi khuda aur is ka rasool tumahray amlon ko ( aur ) dekhen ge phir tum gayab o hazir ke jan-nay walay ( khuday-e wahid ) ki taraf lout’tay jao ge aur jo amal tum karte rahay ho woh sab tumhe betaye ga
9,95,jab tum un ke paas lout kar jao ge to tumahray rubaroo khuda ki kasmain khayen ge taakay tum un se dar guzar karo so unn ki taraf iltifaat nah karna. yeh napak hain aur jo yeh kaam karte rahay hain is ke badla un ka thikana dozakh hai
9,96,yeh tumahray agay kasmain khayen ge taakay tum un se khush ho jao lekin agar tum unn se khush ho jao ge to khuda to nafarman logon se khush nahi hota
9,97,dehati log sakht kafir aur sakht munhafiq hain aur is qabil hain ke jo ehkaam ( Shariat ) khuda ne apne rasool par nazil farmaiye hain un se waaqif ( hi ) nah hon. aur khuda jan-nay wala ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
9,98,aur baaz dehati aisay hain ke jo kharch karte hain usay tawwan samajte hain aur tumahray haq mein musibaton ke munhtazir hain. un hi par buri museebat ( waqay ) ho. aur khuda suneney wala ( aur ) jan-nay wala hai
9,99,aur baaz dehati aisay hain ke khuda par aur roz akhirat par imaan rakhtay hain aur jo kuch kharch karte hain is ko khuda ki Qurbat aur paighambar ki duaon ka zareya samajte hain. dekho woh be shuba un ke liye ( mojab ) qurbat hai khuda un ko anqareeb apni rehmat mein daakhil kere ga. be shak khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
